\begin_inset Formula $z_{0}=\textcolor{purple}{\ensuremath{r}}_{0}\cdot e^{i\cdot\textcolor{green}{\ensuremath{\vartheta}}_{0}}$
\end_inset

 due numeri complessi in forma polare.
