\begin_layout Standard
La formula del cambiamento di base lega queste due matrici:
 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
[f]_{\mathcal{\textcolor{blue}{\ensuremath{C}}}}^{\textcolor{blue}{\ensuremath{\mathcal{C}}}}=[\text{id}_{V}]_{\mathcal{\textcolor{blue}{\ensuremath{\mathcal{C}}}}}^{\textcolor{magenta}{\ensuremath{\mathcal{B}}}}\cdot[f]_{\textcolor{magenta}{\ensuremath{\mathcal{B}}}}^{\textcolor{magenta}{\ensuremath{\mathcal{B}}}}\cdot[\text{id}_{V}]_{\textcolor{magenta}{\ensuremath{\mathcal{B}}}}^{\mathcal{\textcolor{blue}{\ensuremath{\mathcal{C}}}}}
\]

\end_inset

Osserviamo che 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
