\begin_inset Formula $A=[f]_{\mathcal{\textcolor{blue}{\ensuremath{C}}}}^{\textcolor{blue}{\ensuremath{\mathcal{C}}}},B=[f]_{\textcolor{magenta}{\ensuremath{\mathcal{B}}}}^{\textcolor{magenta}{\ensuremath{\mathcal{B}}}}$
\end_inset

